National director of the Youth Mobilisation North West and APC zonal secretary, Rt.Hon Bello Muhammad Goronyo has said the APC presidential candidate Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu and his running mate Kashim Shettima will unlock the potentials inherent in the Northern part of the country.
Goronyo who stated this while calling on Nigerians particularly Youth in the North West region to vote Tinubu/Shettima, said the candidates have the capacity to turn things around.
He described Tinubu as an innovator who is ready to engage experts and technocrats as well as deploy latest techniques and technologies to solve problems of insecurity, Education, Health, infrastructural deficit and execute projects at a record time.
Goronyo, who stated this while granting an interview at an APC rally in Gusau, Zamfara State, added that the APC under President Muhammadu Buhari has done well and that Tinubu will consolidate on the achievements of the party if voted into office as Buhari’s successor.
“I therefore call on all and sundry to vote for the presidential candidate of the APC Asiwaju Ahmed Bola Tinubu and his competent running mate Senator Kashim Shettima for a better Nigeria”.
He further described the combination of the two as a perfect match that will lead Nigerians to it’s promised land, adding that we must not fall into the traps of the People Democratic Party (PDP) or any other party.
“Let me also call on every eligible voter who is yet to pick up their PVCs to take advantage of the extension to do so,because that is your power to vote for credible candidates such as Asiwaju Ahmed Bola Tinubu and Kashim Shettima” he stressed.